Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:28.82,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}闔上雙目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:32.26,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}罪孽深重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:35.17,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:46.14,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你的氣味 令人發狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:50.14,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}真夜中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:53.30,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}瘋狂 愛 一併飲乾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:56.34,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}投入這臂彎中吧
