Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:05.27,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你惶然不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:08.90,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}即將要迎來永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:12.15,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}"這邊的黑暗是甜美的"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:18.37,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}我深深地刺入
